l help to financial services companies to develop \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2  policies.\par \par \uc2 "They are recognition that these issues are an important dimension in doing business these days," the ABI said.\par \par \uc2 The guidelines, drawn up by the Forge group, are independent of the so-called London Principles set to be unveiled by Tony Blair at the Johannesburg \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2  summit, but do overlap them. The London Principles are expected to set out criteria for "sustainable finance".\par \par \uc2 The Forge group was chaired by Aviva and includes Abbey National, Barclays, Legal &General, Lloyds TSB, Royal Bank of Scotland, Royal & Sun Alliance and Zurich. PwC, the professional services firm, acted as adviser to the group.\par \par \uc2 After a discussion period, the guidelines will be launched on November 5 by Stephen Timms, minister for e-commerce and competitiveness.\par \par \uc2 London Edition 1. \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b NS\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 c13 : \uc2 Regulation/Government Policy | ccat : \uc2 Corporate/Industrial News\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b RE\b0\cell \pard \ql \