alpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b LP\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Romano Prodi, Commission president, will take part in a high-level banking meeting in Frankfurt on Friday.\par \par \uc2 The European Banking Congress is set to discuss the latest developments in EU financial services legislation. Mr Prodi is expected to update some of Europe's most important banks on Europe's progress towards a new constitution.\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Other items on the agenda include include new developments in regulation for the world's stock exchanges.\par \par \uc2 Baron Alexandre Lamfalussy, the former Belgian central banker who designed a new fast track system to approve EU financial law, Werner Seifert, Deutsche Borse chief executive officer and Hardwick Simmons, Nasdaq chief executive will take part in the debate.\par \par \uc2 Tussle over chemicals policy\par \par \uc2 Elsewhere, a meeting in Copenhagen will discuss the highly sensitive subject of EU chemicals policy. The meeting, at the level of "competent authorities", occurs as the European Commission prepares legislation to deal with the 99 per cent of chemical products circulating in the EU that lack thorough authorisation.\par \par \uc2 While Green groups say that a systematic process of testing and authorisation is essential, German industrial gatherings argue that some 2.3million jobs could be at stake if the legislation is too heavy handed. The meeting on Friday will be aimed at ensuring "continuity and coherence in the work on new and existing substances." At the practical level the debate hinges on how great the scope for exemptions will be.\par \par \uc2 In light of this, the European \b \highlight22\uc2 Environment\b0 \highlight\uc2  Agency will present a report "Late Lessons from Early Warnings - the precautionary principle from 1896 - 2000", with a special focus on chemicals.\par \par \uc2 There will also be an informal meeting of sports ministers, as well as a gathering of deputies of the influential 133 committee on trade policy.\par \par \uc2 In Denmark, there will be a meeting on \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2 , dealing with the Commission's communication of the same title, which addresses business contributions to sustainable development.\par \par \uc2 There will also be a meeting of water directors in anticipation of new guidelines on the Water Framework Directive. \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b IN\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 i1 : \uc2 Energy | i17 : \uc2 Water Utilities | i25 : \uc2 Chemicals | i814 : \uc2 Banking | ibnk : \uc2 Banking/Credit\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 